    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs(0.97)
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.36 / v2 + 0.34) - (tmp + 0.63 * v2 + 0.80)) - (wp.sin(v2 + 0.79) + (v0 + 0.19 + v0 + 0.54)))
    v0 = (wp.sin(v2) - 0.17)
    v0 = (tmp - wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.88)))
